Chairman Lord Allan Jay Q. Velasco stated that the Committee will come up with a Committee Resolution urging the DOE to fast track the issuance of the directive for the direct downloading of the host communities of the revenues derived from the power generating plants.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON ENERGY ON 2016-09-05</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PREVIOUS COMMITTEE REFERRALS :PRIMARILY REFERRED TO RULES on 2016-08-02;</td></tr></table>